OL,3,CUK's response to Covid 'too little,
OL,4,Ctoo late', inquiry concludes
OL,6,FFour and a half years after Boris
OL,7,FJohnson set up the Covid Inquiry,
OL,8,Fafter hearing evidence from all those
OL,9,Fwho led the UK's Covid response, today
OL,10,Fwe have its verdict.
OL,12,FEight hundred pages of detailed
OL,13,Fevidence can be summed up in one
OL,14,Fsentence: the UK's response was "too
OL,15,Flittle too late".
