OL,3,CUK's response to Covid 'too little,
OL,4,Ctoo late', inquiry concludes
OL,6,FIn a conclusion that will be
OL,7,Fdevastating to those who lost loved
OL,8,Fones during the pandemic, Baroness
OL,9,FHallett, the inquiry chair, states:
OL,10,F"Had the UK been better prepared,
OL,11,Flives would have been saved, suffering
OL,12,Freduced and the economic cost of the
OL,13,Fpandemic far lower."
OL,15,FBoris Johnson's Downing Street does
OL,16,Fnot come out of the inquiry well,
OL,17,Fcriticised for a "toxic and chaotic
OL,18,Fculture" at the centre of government.
