OL,6,FAs for Partygate, she aims another
OL,7,Fblow at that sorry chapter with this:
OL,8,F"Allegations of rule-breaking by
OL,9,Fministers and advisors caused huge
OL,10,Fdistress and undermined public
OL,11,Fconfidence."
OL,13,FBut none of the four UK governments
OL,14,Fescape criticism - all four failed to
OL,15,Fappreciate the scale of the threat or
OL,16,Fthe urgency of response that it
OL,17,Fdemanded.
OL,19,FThe Welsh, Scottish and Northern Irish
OL,20,Fadministrations were also too reliant
OL,21,Fon the UK to lead the response.
