OL,3,CUK's response to Covid 'too little,
OL,4,Ctoo late', inquiry concludes
OL,6,FThe report describes February 2020,
OL,7,Fwhen it was known that the virus was
OL,8,Fspreading around the world and had
OL,9,Freached the UK, as a "lost month" with
OL,10,Fthe failure of all four governments to
OL,11,Fmake adequate preparations as
OL,12,F"inexplicable".
OL,14,FBy 12 March, the day Boris Johnson
OL,15,Fwarned the public: "I must level with
OL,16,Fyou ...many more families are going to
OL,17,Flose loved ones before their time",
OL,18,Fthe situation had become, according to
OL,19,FBaroness Hallett, "calamitous" and
OL,20,F"any opportunity to get on top of the
OL,21,Fvirus had been lost".
