OL,3,CUK's response to Covid 'too little,
OL,4,Ctoo late', inquiry concludes
OL,6,FThe lockdowns of 2020 and 2021, which
OL,7,Fshut schools, isolated care homes and
OL,8,Fdivided families, only became
OL,9,Finevitable, Baroness Hallett
OL,10,Fconcludes, "because of the acts and
OL,11,Fomissions of the four governments".
OL,13,FChair of the Inquiry, Baroness
OL,14,FHallett, said "all four governments
OL,15,Ffailed to appreciate the scale of the
OL,16,Fthreat or the urgency of the response
OL,17,Fit demanded in the early part of 2020"
