OL,3,CUK's response to Covid 'too little,
OL,4,Ctoo late', inquiry concludes
OL,6,FIn conclusion, she believes tighter
OL,7,Frestrictions should have been imposed
OL,8,Fearlier in March, and having failed to
OL,9,Fdo that, a complete lockdown should
OL,10,Fhave been imposed a week earlier than
OL,11,Fit eventually was.
OL,13,FHad Boris Johnson done that, modelling
OL,14,Fsuggests there would have been around
OL,15,F23, 000 fewer deaths in England alone.
OL,17,FIt's not just the delay in
OL,18,Fimplementing lockdowns that comes
OL,19,Funder fire.
