OL,6,FThere was too little thought given to
OL,7,Fhow restrictions would impact
OL,8,Fvulnerable groups, the impact of
OL,9,Fschool closures on pupils' mental
OL,10,Fhealth and education, and the
OL,11,Fcomplexity of the regulations made it
OL,12,Fdifficult for the public to understand
OL,13,Fwhich rules applied to them.
OL,15,FBaroness Hallett makes a set of
OL,16,Fdetailed recommendations that include:
OL,18,FFor this lengthy, multimillion-pound
OL,19,Finquiry to have been worth it, the
OL,20,Fcurrent government had better take
OL,21,Fnote.
